view.name: Mobile Phone Masts In Camden
view.description: This dataset contains the location of mobile phone masts in Camden. Data is provided annually by the MOA (Mobile Operators Association). Attribution includes the operator name, site address and ward name. Some sites are duplicated where operators share the same infrastructure.
